column16: David Murphy lines out to right fielder Ichiro Suzuki.
Carlos Santana homers (14) on a line drive to right field.    Michael Brantley scores.
Michael Brantley singles on a sharp ground ball to center fielder Jacoby Ellsbury, deflected by shortstop Derek Jeter.   Jason Kipnis scores.
Asdrubal Cabrera flies out to center fielder Jacoby Ellsbury.
Jason Kipnis singles on a line drive to center fielder Jacoby Ellsbury.
Umpire reviewed (home run), call on the field was overturned: Roberto Perez homers (1) on a fly ball to left center field.   Chris Dickerson scores.
Chris Dickerson doubles (1) on a line drive to right fielder Ichiro Suzuki.
David Murphy strikes out on a foul tip.
Lonnie Chisenhall singles on a ground ball to center fielder Jacoby Ellsbury.
Carlos Santana lines out to second baseman Brendan Ryan.
Kendrys Morales grounds into a double play, third baseman Zelous Wheeler to first baseman Mark Teixeira.   Chris Colabello out at 2nd.
Trevor Plouffe homers (6) on a fly ball to left center field.
Kurt Suzuki flies out to right fielder Ichiro Suzuki.
